### Test HTTP para CRUD de Recetas
### Reemplaza {admin_token} con un token JWT válido de usuario ADMIN

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@adminToken = tu_token_admin_aqui

### ============ 1. CREAR RECETA: HAMBURGUESA ============

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hamburguesa Premium",
  "quantity": 1,
  "description": "Hamburguesa deliciosa con ingredientes de calidad",
  "itemDetails": [
    {
      "itemId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "annotation": "pan tostado",
      "isOptional": false
    },
    {
      "itemId": 2,
      "quantity": 150,
      "annotation": "bien cocida",
      "isOptional": false
    },
    {
      "itemId": 3,
      "quantity": 1,
      "annotation": "queso cheddar",
      "isOptional": false
    },
    {
      "itemId": 4,
      "quantity": 2,
      "annotation": "rodajas de tomate",
      "isOptional": true
    },
    {
      "itemId": 5,
      "quantity": 1,
      "annotation": "hoja de lechuga",
      "isOptional": true
    }
  ]
}

### Guardar el ID de la respuesta (ej: 1)

