### ============ 4. OBTENER TODAS LAS RECETAS ============

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============ 5. OBTENER RECETA POR ID (ID=1) ============

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============ 6. OBTENER RECETA POR ID (ID=2) ============

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

